ActPublic Sector Pension Investment Board Act
PrecisAppointment of HELEN MALLOVY-HICKS of Toronto, Ontario, to be a director of the Public Sector Pension Investment Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of four years, in the place of Garnet Garven, whose term has expired.
